=== Cultural properties ===
=== Important Cultural Property ===
* Omiashi Shrine stone stupa, with associated offering implements (small glass jar, qingbai lidded container, four-eared jar with lid) - the eleven-tier stone pagoda. Designated on April 5, {{ill|lt=1909|Q2057|WD=Q2057|1=1909}} ({{ill|lt=Meiji|Q3125096|WD=Q3125096|1=Meiji era}} 42); associated items additionally designated on June 17, {{ill|lt=1970|Q2474|WD=Q2474|1=1970}} ({{ill|lt=Showa|Q327567|WD=Q327567|1=Shōwa era}} 45)<ref>{{Cite web|和書|url= https://asukamura.jp/bunkazai/shiteibunkazai_11.html |title=Cultural Properties |publisher=Asuka Village |accessdate=2019-09-13 }}</ref>.

